[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis Summary[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the evaluation report and code snippets, the timeout issue persists[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecause the previous patch only added validation for **array sizes** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMAX_SUBRS, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_CHARSTRINGS, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but did not address the **unbounded while loops** that [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearch for specific tokens. The root causes are:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Primary Root Causes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mParser-level[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m**: Searches for [0m[32m"dup"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"readonly"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"def"[0m[39m without [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration limit[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lines [0m[1;36m226[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m234[0m[39m**: Processes [0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m entries without iteration [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m563[0m[39m**: Searches for [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m token without iteration [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m643[0m[39m**: Searches for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m token without [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration limit[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Secondary Root Causes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLexer-level[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: No limit on string length, can process entire [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: No limit on token length[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readComment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: No limit on comment length[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: do-while structure can loop with corrupted input[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why Previous Patch Failed:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch added `Type1ParserLimits` class with MAX_SUBRS, MAX_CHARSTRINGS, etc., [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand validated array sizes. However, it did NOT protect the while loops that [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**search for tokens**. Malicious input can contain thousands of tokens before [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreaching the expected token [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor never reaching it[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, causing the parser to loop [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough all tokens until timeout.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Add Loop Iteration Limits[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDefine new constants in `Type1ParserLimits` class [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor add a new class for parser [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstants[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclass Type1ParserLimits [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    static final int MAX_SUBRS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    static final int MAX_CHARSTRINGS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    static final int MAX_ENCODING_ENTRIES = [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    static final int MAX_OTHERSUBRS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m NEW: Loop iteration limits[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    static final int MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Maximum iterations when [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearching for tokens[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    static final int MAX_STRING_LENGTH = 1_000_000;    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Maximum [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstring/comment/token length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m1MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    static final int MAX_NESTING_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m;          [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Maximum array/procedure [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnesting depth[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Protect Parser While Loops with Iteration Counters[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - First while loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd iteration counter before the loop and check it inside:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Search for encoding start tokens[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken currentToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentToken != null && [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m &&[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcurrentToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ||[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mcurrentToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ||[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mcurrentToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while searching for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mencoding start"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    currentToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentToken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of tokens while searching for encoding [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mstart"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - Second while loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m226[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m234[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd iteration counter for the dup-processing loop:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMap<Integer, String> codeToName = new HashMap<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint dupCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    int code = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    String name = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME, [0m[32m"put"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mcodeToName.put[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcode, name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - Private search loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m563[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd iteration counter:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while searching for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mPrivate dictionary"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - CharStrings search loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m643[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd iteration counter:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Protect Lexer Methods with Length Limits[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m432[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m497[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd length check in the while loop:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate Token [0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    StringBuilder sb = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_STRING_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"String token exceeds maximum length: "[0m[39m + [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_STRING_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of the switch statement [0m[33m...[0m                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m379[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m406[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd length check:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate String [0m[1;35mreadRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    StringBuilder sb = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_STRING_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Token exceeds maximum length: "[0m[39m + [0m               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        char c = [0m[1;35mgetChar[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of the logic [0m[33m...[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readComment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m411[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m427[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd length check:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_STRING_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_STRING_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        char c = [0m[1;35mgetChar[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return [0m[1;35msb.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Protect [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Loops with Nesting Depth Limits[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m382[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m417[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd nesting depth check:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate List<Token> [0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    List<Token> value = new ArrayList<>[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Token token = [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return value;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mvalue.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtoken.getKind[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == Token.START_ARRAY[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        int openArray = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        int iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while reading [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32marray"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                return value;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.START_ARRAY[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                openArray++;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mopenArray > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_NESTING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Array nesting depth exceeds maximum: "[0m[39m +[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_NESTING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of the logic [0m[33m...[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of the method [0m[33m...[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### Fix [0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m469[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m536[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd similar iteration and nesting depth checks as in [0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m: Reapply Previous Patch Validations[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch's validation for array sizes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMAX_SUBRS, MAX_CHARSTRINGS, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_ENCODING_ENTRIES, MAX_OTHERSUBRS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m should be **retained** as they provide [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnecessary protection against memory exhaustion. These validations are at:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m738[0m[39m: Subrs count validation[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m772[0m[39m: Subrs index range check[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m796[0m[39m: OtherSubrs count validation[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m824[0m[39m: CharStrings count validation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m224[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39madded in patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Encoding entries validation[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Approach is Optimal:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Defense in Depth**: Protects at multiple levels [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparser loops, lexer loops, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnesting depth[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Preserves Existing Logic**: Does not change the core parsing algorithms, only [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madds guards[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Consistent with Codebase Patterns**: Similar to protection patterns found in:[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `XrefTrailerResolver` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m282[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m285[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Loop size checking[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `XrefParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m106[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Previous value tracking to detect cycles[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `BaseParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m992[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1002[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Progress checking to prevent infinite loops[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `PfbParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m71[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: MAX_LENGTH constant for file size limits[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `ScratchFileBuffer` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m107[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m112[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Overflow protection[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Addresses Root Causes**: The timeout occurs because:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Parser loops can iterate indefinitely searching for tokens[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Lexer methods can accumulate unbounded strings[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No limits on iterations or token sizes[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This fix adds explicit bounds to all these areas.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Minimal Performance Impact**: The iteration counters add negligible overhead [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39msimple integer increment and comparison[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Clear Error Messages**: Throws IOExceptions with descriptive messages [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating which limit was exceeded[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Does Not Modify Harness**: All fixes are in the source code [0m[1;39m([0m[39mType1Parser.java,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Lexer.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, not in test or fuzzing code[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Evaluation Report:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Initial Issue**: libFuzzer timeout - Fixed by preventing infinite loops[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Patch Attempt Result**: Timeout persisted - Previous patch only validated array[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msizes, not loop iterations[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Areas for Further Investigation**: This fix addresses items [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mType1Lexer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mother while loops[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken stream handling[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39minput preprocessing[0m[1;39m)[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate large fonts might be rejected**: [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: The limits are set very high [0m[1;39m([0m[39m100K iterations, 1MB strings[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maccommodate legitimate fonts while blocking DoS attacks[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Error handling changes behavior**:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: The new IOExceptions are consistent with existing error handling [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the parser[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Performance overhead**:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Integer comparisons are extremely fast, negligible impact on [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing time[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Reference to Similar Solutions:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe iteration limit pattern is used extensively in PDFBox:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mXrefTrailerResolver.nextXrefObj[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Uses Set size comparison to limit iterations[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mXrefParser.parseXref[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Uses lastPrev tracking to detect cycles[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mBaseParser.parseObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Checks for empty strings to prevent infinite loops[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe length limit pattern is used in:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `PfbParser`: MAX_LENGTH = 100_000_000 for total file size[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `ScratchFileBuffer`: Checks for integer overflow when growing buffers[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis fix strategy applies these proven patterns consistently across Type1Parser and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Lexer.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a [0m[32m"libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m error, indicating that fuzzing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations on the codebase are encountering execution paths that take excessive [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtime to complete. The patch attempt introduces parsing limits and iteration bounds [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto prevent denial-of-service [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDoS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m attacks in the Type1Parser class. However, the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch fails to compile due to a duplicate variable declaration error: the variable [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`searchIterations` is defined twice within the same method scope in [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue Analysis[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe issue [0m[32m"ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m indicates that during fuzz testing, certain [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs cause the parsing logic to execute for an extended period, exceeding the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer's timeout threshold. This typically occurs when:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- There are unbounded loops that can iterate indefinitely or for an excessive [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnumber of times[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The parser encounters malformed or malicious input that triggers pathological [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- There are no safeguards against deeply nested structures or excessively large [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata collections[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt Details[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduces a new inner class `Type1ParserLimits` with the following [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstants:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_SUBRS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_CHARSTRINGS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_ENCODING_ENTRIES = [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m`[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_OTHERSUBRS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m`[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m1000000[0m[39m`[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `MAX_NESTING_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch modifies several methods in `Type1Parser.java` to add iteration limits [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand bounds checking:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Encoding parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m227[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Adds an iteration counter [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`searchIterations` to limit the search for encoding start tokens [0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"readonly"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Also adds null checks for tokens and validates the number of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mencoding entries against `MAX_ENCODING_ENTRIES`.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Array reading [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m423[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Introduces an `iterations` counter in the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadSimpleValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method to prevent infinite loops when reading arrays. Also adds[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnesting depth checks against `MAX_NESTING_DEPTH`.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Procedure reading [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m513[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Adds iteration limits in the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method with nesting depth validation.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Void procedure reading [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m563[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Similar iteration and nesting [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdepth checks in `[0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Private dictionary search [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m618[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Adds a `searchIterations` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcounter to bound the search for the [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m dictionary token, with null checks.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **CharStrings search [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m711[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Introduces another `searchIterations` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcounter to limit the search for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m token with null checks.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Compilation Error[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe compilation fails with the following error:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m[[0m[39mERROR[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/src/project-parent/pdfbox/fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/[0m[95mType1Pars[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [95mer.java[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m714[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m13[0m[1;39m][0m[39m variable searchIterations is already defined in method [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis error occurs because the patch introduces a variable named `searchIterations` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat two different locations within the same method `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- First at line [0m[1;36m621[0m[39m for searching the Private dictionary[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Second at line [0m[1;36m714[0m[39m for searching CharStrings[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSince both code sections are within the same method scope, the second declaration [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconflicts with the first, causing a compilation failure.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo fully address the timeout issue and create a working patch, the following areas [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof the codebase should be examined:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Method structure of `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`**: Review the complete structure of [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis method to understand the control flow and determine appropriate variable [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscoping or renaming strategies.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Fix the Compilation Error[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Problem**: The variable `searchIterations` is declared twice within [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- First declaration: Around line [0m[1;36m621[0m[39m for searching the [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m token[0m              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Solution**: Use unique variable names for each search loop to avoid scope [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconflicts:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- For Private dictionary search: Use `privateSearchIterations`[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- For CharStrings search: Use `charStringsSearchIterations`[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch must address all unbounded loops and potentially malicious length values.[0m [2m                [0m
