[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter before the loop: `int encodingSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++encodingSearchIterations > [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add null check for `[0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` before accessing `[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if limit exceeded or token is null[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**B2. Private dictionary search loop in `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m557[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter: `int privateSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;` [0m[1;39m([0m[39muse unique name[0m[1;39m)[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++privateSearchIterations > [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maintain the existing null check pattern from the failed patch[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if limit exceeded with descriptive message[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**B3. CharStrings search loop in `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter: `int charStringsSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;` [0m[1;39m([0m[39muse unique name, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdifferent from B2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++charStringsSearchIterations > [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add null check for token before accessing `[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if limit exceeded or token is null[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### C. Add Encoding Entries Counter [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m location[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**In `[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m226[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m234[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add counter before the while loop: `int encodingEntryCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++encodingEntryCount > [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_ENCODING_ENTRIES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException if too many encoding entries[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This prevents unbounded reading of [0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m entries[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### D. Validate Length Parameters [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[39m locations[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**D1. In `[0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m709[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After reading length: `int length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add validation: [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_SUBRS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid Subrs length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**D2. In `[0m[1;35mreadOtherSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m759[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After reading length: `int length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add validation:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_OTHERSUBRS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid OtherSubrs length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**D3. In `[0m[1;35mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m779[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After reading length: `int length = [0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.INTEGER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.intValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add validation:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || length > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_CHARSTRINGS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid CharStrings length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#### E. Add Iteration and Nesting Limits to Nested Structure Reading [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[39m locations[0m[1;39m)[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**E1. In `[0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` array reading [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m392[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m417[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter before while loop: `int iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m396[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After incrementing `openArray` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m403[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mopenArray > [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_NESTING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw appropriate IOExceptions for both conditions[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**E2. In `[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m469[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m505[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter before while loop: `int iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m476[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After incrementing `openProc` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m483[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mopenProc > [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_NESTING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw appropriate IOExceptions for both conditions[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**E3. In `[0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m510[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m536[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add iteration counter before while loop: `int iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m516[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After incrementing `openProc` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m521[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Check `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mopenProc > [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1ParserLimits.MAX_NESTING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw appropriate IOExceptions for both conditions[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Details[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Pattern for Search Loops:**[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint uniqueSearchName = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken currentToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentToken != null && ![0m[1;35mmatchesExpectedToken[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentToken[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++uniqueSearchName > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while searching for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m[[0m[32mtoken name[0m[32m][0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    currentToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentToken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of tokens while searching for [0m[32m[[0m[32mtoken [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mname[0m[32m][0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Pattern for Nested Structure Reading:**[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint iterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++iterations > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while reading [0m[32m[[0m[32mstructure[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mtype[0m[32m][0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing null checks[0m[33m...[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnestingCounter > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_NESTING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"[0m[32m[[0m[32mStructure type[0m[32m][0m[32m nesting depth exceeds maximum: "[0m[39m + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            Type1ParserLimits.MAX_NESTING_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m rest of loop logic[0m[33m...[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Addresses Compilation Error**: Using unique variable names [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`privateSearchIterations`, `charStringsSearchIterations`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m eliminates the duplicate[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclaration error while maintaining clear, descriptive naming.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Comprehensive Timeout Prevention**: The strategy addresses all identified [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout vectors:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Unbounded search loops [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[39m locations[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Unbounded entry reading [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m location[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Malicious length values [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[39m locations[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Unbounded nested structure reading [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[39m locations[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Preserves Existing Logic**: All modifications add validation guards without [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchanging the core parsing logic. Early exit conditions and token reading patterns [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain unchanged.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Follows Codebase Patterns**: [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Uses named constants for limits [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike `MAX_CACHED_PAGES` in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRandomAccessReadBufferedFile[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException with descriptive messages [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconsistent with existing error [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandling[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Validates against Integer.MAX_VALUE overflow [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike ScratchFileBuffer[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Uses iteration counting pattern [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike XrefTrailerResolver[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **No Harness or Test Modifications**: The fix only modifies Type1Parser.java, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleaving fuzzing infrastructure and test code untouched. The fuzzer can continue [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtesting with the same API surface.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Defense in Depth**: Multiple layers of protection:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Iteration limits prevent infinite loops[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Length validation prevents resource exhaustion[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Nesting depth limits prevent stack overflow[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Null checks prevent NPE crashes[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate Large Fonts**: The chosen limits [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m for subrs/charstrings, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m for iterations[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are generous enough for legitimate fonts while preventing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDoS attacks. These values are significantly higher than typical Type [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m fonts [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequire.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Early Termination**: Malformed but non-malicious fonts might be rejected. This[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis acceptable as they violate format expectations and could indicate corruption.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Performance Impact**: The additional checks add minimal overhead [0m[1;39m([0m[39msimple [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteger comparisons[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and won't affect normal parsing performance.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix is optimal because it systematically addresses all timeout vectors while [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaintaining backward compatibility with legitimate fonts and following established [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFBox patterns for security validation.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a libFuzzer timeout error occurring in the Apache PDFBox [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox component. A patch was attempted that introduced parsing limits and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration guards in the Type1Parser class to prevent potential infinite loops and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdenial-of-service [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDoS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m attacks. However, after applying the patch, the timeout [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror persists, indicating that the patch did not successfully resolve the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munderlying timeout issue.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a libFuzzer timeout error with no additional context provided.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis type of error typically indicates that the fuzzing process encountered an [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput that caused the code to execute for an extended period, exceeding the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfigured timeout threshold. The timeout suggests the presence of either an [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loop, an extremely inefficient algorithm, or a computationally expensive [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperation that doesn't complete within the expected timeframe.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduces several defensive mechanisms to the Type1Parser class:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **New Limits Class**: A `Type1ParserLimits` inner class is defined with the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfollowing constants:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_SUBRS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_CHARSTRINGS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_ENCODING_ENTRIES = [0m[1;36m256[0m[39m`[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_OTHERSUBRS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m`[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_STRING_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m1000000[0m[39m`[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `MAX_NESTING_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m`[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Encoding Search Protection** [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m227[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds an iteration counter `encodingSearchIterations` to the while loop that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearches for encoding start markers[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks if iterations exceed `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS` and throws an IOException [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif exceeded[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds null checking for `currentToken` and throws an exception if the token [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream ends unexpectedly[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds an `encodingEntryCount` counter that limits the number of encoding [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries to `MAX_ENCODING_ENTRIES`[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Array Reading Protection** [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m424[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds an iteration counter to the array reading loop[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks if iterations exceed `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS`[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds nesting depth checking for arrays, limiting to `MAX_NESTING_DEPTH`[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Procedure Reading Protection** [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m471[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m514[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds iteration counters to both `[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` methods[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks if iterations exceed `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS`[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds nesting depth checking for procedures, limiting to `MAX_NESTING_DEPTH`[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Private Dictionary Search Protection** [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m619[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds an iteration counter `privateSearchIterations` to the loop searching for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe Private dictionary[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks if iterations exceed `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS`[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **CharStrings Search Protection** [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m707[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds an iteration counter `charStringsSearchIterations` to the loop searching [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor CharStrings[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks if iterations exceed `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS`[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Adds null checking for `charStringsToken` and throws an exception if the token[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream ends unexpectedly[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Result[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the libFuzzer timeout error persists. This indicates [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The timeout is not occurring in any of the protected loops, OR[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The iteration limits set [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparticularly `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill too high and allow sufficient iterations to cause a timeout, OR[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The timeout is occurring in a different part of the code that was not addressed [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby this patch[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas Requiring Further Investigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Type1Lexer Class**: The patch modifies Type1Parser but relies heavily on the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlexer [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvia `[0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The timeout could be [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurring within the lexer's tokenization logic itself.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Unprotected Loops**: There may be other loops in the Type1Parser class that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwere not covered by this patch, or loops in related classes that process Type1 [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfonts.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Iteration Limit Calibration**: The `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS` value of [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmay still be too high. If the fuzzer input triggers close to this many iterations, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit could still cause a timeout depending on the work performed in each iteration.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Token Processing Complexity**: Each call to `[0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` may involve complex processing. If the input causes these [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations to become expensive, even a reasonable number of iterations could lead [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto timeouts.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **CharString Processing**: The patch adds protection up to the point of finding [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCharStrings, but the actual processing of CharStrings data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m707[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is not [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshown and may contain the timeout-causing code.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Subrs and OtherSubrs Processing**: While limits are defined for `MAX_SUBRS` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `MAX_OTHERSUBRS`, the patch doesn't show these limits being enforced anywhere [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the code, suggesting there may be other sections of the parser that need similar[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotection.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Input-Specific Patterns**: The fuzzer may be generating specific input [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatterns that trigger pathological behavior not covered by the iteration guards, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuch as deeply nested structures, excessively long tokens, or specific combinations[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof font directives.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
