[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m978[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCharacter.digit[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m by, [0m[1;36m16[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m979[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m980[0m[39m:                ++len;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m981[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m982[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m983[0m[39m:        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m res = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mlen [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m984[0m[39m:        int r = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m985[0m[39m:        int prev = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m986[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte by : bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m987[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m988[0m[39m:            int digit = [0m[1;35mCharacter.digit[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mchar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m by, [0m[1;36m16[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m989[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdigit != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m990[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m991[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m992[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m993[0m[39m:                    prev = digit;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m994[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m995[0m[39m:                else[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m996[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m997[0m[39m:                    res[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mr++[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprev * [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m + digit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m998[0m[39m:                    prev = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m999[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1000[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1001[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1002[0m[39m:        return res;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1003[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the code and evaluation report, I've identified the primary root [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause of the persistent timeout:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Primary Issue: No Size Limit on Input Data**[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m69[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m only checks `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msegment2.length > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout an upper bound[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A malicious fuzzer can provide arbitrarily large segment2 data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmegabytes or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgigabytes[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This unlimited data flows through expensive operations:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `[0m[1;35mhexToBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - iterates through entire array twice[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `[0m[1;35mdecrypt[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - iterates through entire array[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `Type1Lexer` - wraps in ByteBuffer with unbounded tokenization loops[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Secondary Issue: Unbounded Lexer Loops**[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe Type1Lexer has multiple unbounded loops that iterate through the entire buffer:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Main tokenization loop with `while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mreadRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Reads tokens with no length limit[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mreadComment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Reads comments with no guarantee of newlines[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: Reads strings with no termination guarantee[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Why Previous Patch Failed:**[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch added iteration guards to parser-level loops [0m[1;39m([0m[39mencoding search, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marray reading, procedure reading, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Did NOT limit the input data size [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprimary root cause[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Did NOT protect the lexer's internal unbounded loops[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Even with parser iteration limits, if each `[0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call processes [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmegabytes of data, timeouts still occur[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. The lexer processes the entire buffer regardless of parser-level guards[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Cascading Effect:**[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Huge segment2 [0m[1;39m([0m[39mGB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m passes validation → Primary issue[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Creates huge ByteBuffer in lexer → Enables long loops  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Parser search loops call lexer many times → Multiplies the problem[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Each lexer call has unbounded internal loops → Final amplification[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Result: Millions/billions of iterations = timeout[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix must address the issue at multiple levels, with primary focus on preventing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive input data:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Add Size Validation in [0m[1;35mType1Parser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPrimary Fix[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.java`[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd a size limit constant following the pattern established by [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH`:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After line [0m[1;36m49[0m[39m, add constant[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_SEGMENT_LENGTH = 50_000_000; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m MB[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Justification for [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m MB limit:**[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- PfbParser uses [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB for total font size [0m[1;39m([0m[39mall segments combined[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Real-world test examples: OpenSans-Regular segment2 = [0m[1;36m96[0m[39m KB, DejaVuSerifCondensed[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegment2 = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m MB[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m MB is generous for segment2 alone while preventing fuzzer abuse[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Well above legitimate fonts but low enough to prevent timeouts[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd validation in `[0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method before line [0m[1;36m69[0m[39m:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Before the segment2 length check at line [0m[1;36m69[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39msegment1.length > MAX_SEGMENT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Type1 font segment1 too large: "[0m[39m + segment1.length + [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                         [0m[32m" bytes [0m[32m([0m[32mmax: "[0m[39m + MAX_SEGMENT_LENGTH + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39msegment2.length > MAX_SEGMENT_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Type1 font segment2 too large: "[0m[39m + segment2.length + [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                         [0m[32m" bytes [0m[32m([0m[32mmax: "[0m[39m + MAX_SEGMENT_LENGTH + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add Iteration Guards to Unprotected Parser Loops [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSecondary Fix[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch attempted to add guards but may have applied them incorrectly or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto wrong line numbers. Ensure these loops are protected:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location A:** `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - Search for [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m token [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Add before the while loop at line [0m[1;36m556[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint privateSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken != null && ![0m[32m"Private"[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpeekToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++privateSearchIterations > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while searching for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mPrivate dictionary"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location B:** `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - Search for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m token [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Add before the while loop at line [0m[1;36m640[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint charStringsSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken charStringsToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcharStringsToken != null && [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcharStringsToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++charStringsSearchIterations > Type1ParserLimits.MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations while searching for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mCharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    charStringsToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcharStringsToken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of tokens while searching for [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mCharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Add Length Limits to Lexer Token Reading [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDefense-in-Depth[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.java`[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd a constant for maximum token length:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After the class declaration, add constant[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH = 1_000_000; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m MB[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Protect `[0m[1;35mreadRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m379[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m406[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate String [0m[1;35mreadRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    StringBuilder sb = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Token too long: "[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[32m" bytes [0m[32m([0m[32mmax: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"[0m[39m + MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mbuffer.mark[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        char c = [0m[1;35mgetChar[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCharacter.isWhitespace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ||[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            c == [0m[32m'[0m[32m([0m[32m'[0m[39m || c == [0m[32m'[0m[32m)[0m[32m'[0m[39m ||[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            c == [0m[32m'<'[0m[39m || c == [0m[32m'>'[0m[39m ||[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            c == [0m[32m'[0m[32m[[0m[32m'[0m[39m || c == [0m[32m'[0m[32m][0m[32m'[0m[39m ||[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            c == [0m[32m'[0m[32m{[0m[32m'[0m[39m || c == [0m[32m'[0m[32m}[0m[32m'[0m[39m ||[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            c == [0m[32m'/'[0m[39m || c == [0m[32m'%'[0m[39m [0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mbuffer.reset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            break;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        else[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35msb.append[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return null;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return [0m[1;35msb.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Protect `[0m[1;35mreadComment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m411[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m427[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate String [0m[1;35mreadComment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    StringBuilder sb = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Comment too long: "[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[32m" bytes [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m([0m[32mmax: "[0m[39m + MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        char c = [0m[1;35mgetChar[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc == [0m[32m'\r'[0m[39m || c == [0m[32m'\n'[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            break;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        else[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35msb.append[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return [0m[1;35msb.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Protect `[0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m432[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m497[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate Token [0m[1;35mreadString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    StringBuilder sb = new [0m[1;35mStringBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbuffer.hasRemaining[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"String too long: "[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msb.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[32m" bytes [0m[32m([0m[32mmax:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"[0m[39m + MAX_TOKEN_LENGTH + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        char c = [0m[1;35mgetChar[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of the method unchanged[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return null;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Reapply Previous Patch Protections[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch added important protections that should be retained if not [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready present:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Encoding search protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m227[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Array reading protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m424[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Procedure reading protection [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines [0m[1;36m471[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m514[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThese should be reapplied with the Type1ParserLimits class if they're not already [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the codebase.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Why This Strategy Works:**[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Prevents Root Cause:** The [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m MB segment limit stops excessively large input [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata before any processing begins, directly preventing the timeout[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Follows Existing Patterns:** The approach mirrors `PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH` [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and other size validation patterns in the codebase[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Defense in Depth:** Multiple layers of protection:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Input validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mprimary defense[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Parser iteration guards [0m[1;39m([0m[39msecondary defense[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Lexer token limits [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtertiary defense[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Preserves Functionality:** [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m MB is far more than any legitimate Type1 font [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mneeds [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreal fonts are typically < [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m MB for segment2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so no valid fonts are [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrejected[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Clear Error Messages:** Provides descriptive IOException messages indicating [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhat limit was exceeded and why[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **No Breaking Changes:** [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Doesn't modify fuzzing logic or harness code[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Doesn't change external APIs[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Doesn't affect test code[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only adds validation that prevents pathological inputs[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Potential Side Effects:**[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Extremely large [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbut potentially legitimate[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m fonts > [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m MB would be rejected[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Mitigation: The limit can be adjusted if legitimate use cases are found; [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m MB is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchosen as a very conservative upper bound[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Why Previous Approaches Failed:**[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch focused only on parser-level iteration limits, but the timeout [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs primarily in the lexer's unbounded loops processing huge input buffers. [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWithout limiting input size first, even guarded parser loops can cause timeouts [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecause each lexer call processes massive amounts of data.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
